            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>There is no legislation governing access to diplomatic records.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers should write directly to the Ministry of Foreign Affairs to inquire
                    about access to diplomatic records. Pre-independence records may be found in
                    France.</p>
            </div>
